// content : ABA Problem

/////////////////////////////////////////

Thread 1 : Stack A-B-C; top = A, next = B

/////////////////////////////////////////

Thread 2 : Stack A-B-C; pop

Thread 2 : Stack   B-C; pop

Thread 2 : Stack     C; push(A)

Thread 2 : Stack   A-C;

/////////////////////////////////////////

Thread 1 : Stack   A-C; top = A, next = B

/////////////////////////////////////////